WEBVTT

01:37.920 --> 01:41.009
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.060 --> 01:43.900
[Episode 16]

01:47.759 --> 01:48.310
Mr. Ji.

01:49.229 --> 01:52.310
Mr. Feng is the head
of the HSKP Department after all.

01:52.310 --> 01:54.000
Making a decision

01:54.420 --> 01:57.039
on his position all by yourself—

01:57.150 --> 01:58.840
isn't that a bit too hasty?

01:58.840 --> 01:59.509
Exactly.

01:59.870 --> 02:01.430
You should at least

02:01.510 --> 02:03.170
discuss it with Mr. Wei first.

02:03.250 --> 02:04.650
So what you're saying is,

02:04.890 --> 02:06.070
the hotel's general manager

02:06.070 --> 02:08.800
can't make personnel
decisions independently?

02:10.150 --> 02:11.190
Or do you think

02:11.190 --> 02:13.610
I should present Mr. Feng's
record of dereliction of duty

02:13.610 --> 02:15.920
directly to the board,

02:16.570 --> 02:18.829
and let Chairman Wei decide personally?

02:29.090 --> 02:30.460
Any other opinions?

02:38.780 --> 02:39.640
Susan, please ask

02:39.640 --> 02:41.990
the HR Department to hire
a new HSKP director as soon as possible.

02:41.990 --> 02:42.990
Okay, Mr. Ji.

02:46.760 --> 02:47.890
Meeting adjourned.

03:27.850 --> 03:29.220
Don't drink in my car.

03:30.730 --> 03:33.170
Zhigang, you have to help me.

03:34.810 --> 03:36.050
How many times have I told you?

03:36.050 --> 03:38.310
Clean up your mess when you do something.

03:38.470 --> 03:39.910
Now that someone's got dirt on you,

03:39.910 --> 03:40.910
how can I help you?

03:40.930 --> 03:41.860
So...

03:41.890 --> 03:43.470
So you're just going to
let that guy Ji Feng

03:43.470 --> 03:44.630
walk all over you?

03:45.120 --> 03:46.680
Stay calm.

03:47.010 --> 03:49.890
He couldn't hold back
and went after my people first.

03:49.890 --> 03:52.420
Don't blame me
for being ruthless from now on.

03:52.850 --> 03:55.579
I've arranged for you
to work at a friend's hotel.

03:56.440 --> 03:57.700
And as for your sister,

03:58.120 --> 03:59.650
you know what to say, right?

04:12.370 --> 04:15.430
I didn't expect Ji Feng
to be serious this time.

04:16.589 --> 04:18.589
Kaixin really took a fall this time.

04:19.120 --> 04:21.769
We both need
to keep a low profile from now on.

04:24.560 --> 04:25.360
Mr. Qian.

04:25.510 --> 04:26.510
What's up?

04:27.310 --> 04:28.600
Can we talk in private?

04:30.090 --> 04:32.270
Mr. Huang and I have something to discuss.

04:32.270 --> 04:33.470
Come back later.

04:34.200 --> 04:34.880
Okay.

04:38.560 --> 04:39.870
Isn't she your subordinate?

04:39.870 --> 04:41.680
Could she be working for Ji Feng?

04:42.950 --> 04:44.830
She works for whoever pays her.

04:44.830 --> 04:46.270
My subordinate?

04:46.580 --> 04:48.700
She'll just use me and kick me away.

04:49.370 --> 04:51.170
Anyway, be careful.

04:51.190 --> 04:52.920
Don't let her set a trap for you.

04:54.390 --> 04:55.830
She wants to play me?

04:56.870 --> 04:58.530
She's a bit too green for that.

05:02.490 --> 05:03.160
Come in.

05:05.820 --> 05:06.620
Mr. Ji.

05:09.680 --> 05:11.780
You took Marcos to the airport?

05:11.860 --> 05:12.630
Yes, I did.

05:12.830 --> 05:13.830
Ms. Lu didn't go?

05:14.040 --> 05:15.120
She said she was busy

05:15.120 --> 05:16.920
and asked me to take him instead.

05:16.950 --> 05:18.240
Did Marcos say anything

05:18.240 --> 05:19.120
before he left?

05:19.800 --> 05:21.440
Nothing special,

05:21.470 --> 05:22.810
just some words of thanks.

05:22.810 --> 05:24.140
What exactly did he say?

05:25.270 --> 05:26.870
He said our service

05:26.870 --> 05:28.510
made him feel at home.

05:30.270 --> 05:32.000
He also said he hopes his employees

05:32.000 --> 05:33.720
can enjoy our service too.

05:36.000 --> 05:37.720
Okay. Thanks for your hard work.

05:37.720 --> 05:39.120
Go back and get some rest.

05:46.600 --> 05:47.390
Mr. Qian.

05:48.870 --> 05:50.830
Go ahead. What is it?

05:51.070 --> 05:52.270
Ms. Lu.

05:52.830 --> 05:55.420
Mr. Qian, I'll be straightforward.

05:55.440 --> 05:56.920
I volunteered this time

05:56.940 --> 05:58.920
not to suck up to the new leader.

05:58.920 --> 05:59.850
On the contrary,

06:00.090 --> 06:01.950
I did it to test the waters for you.

06:02.720 --> 06:04.800
Ms. Lu, what do you mean?

06:05.660 --> 06:07.420
I know the current situation

06:07.450 --> 06:09.050
isn't what you hoped for.

06:09.080 --> 06:11.000
But if you want to hold onto

06:11.000 --> 06:12.720
the No.1 spot in sales,

06:12.960 --> 06:15.900
someone has to step up
and take on this task.

06:16.050 --> 06:17.360
I'm giving it my all

06:17.390 --> 06:19.650
for our sales department's reputation,

06:19.690 --> 06:21.900
not to work for Mr. Ji.

06:22.640 --> 06:24.960
Mr. Qian, please believe me.

06:24.990 --> 06:26.970
I'm definitely on your side.

06:27.050 --> 06:28.610
I took the lead in this event

06:28.630 --> 06:30.250
just to test the waters for you

06:30.250 --> 06:31.840
and see how deep it goes.

06:32.140 --> 06:35.060
I would never betray you.

06:36.790 --> 06:38.650
With you explaining it like this,

06:39.080 --> 06:41.140
it actually makes sense, doesn't it?

06:41.540 --> 06:43.880
Otherwise, I was starting to think Mr. Wei

06:44.230 --> 06:46.430
had sent me an ungrateful wretch.

06:47.130 --> 06:48.360
Mr. Qian, I knew

06:48.390 --> 06:50.360
you must have misunderstood me.

06:50.430 --> 06:52.630
That's why I hurried over to apologize.

06:54.040 --> 06:55.070
Mr. Qian,

06:55.260 --> 06:57.370
I know you like game and wild goods,

06:57.600 --> 06:59.040
so I had someone
custom-order these for you.

06:59.040 --> 07:00.410
Look at you, Ms. Lu.

07:00.510 --> 07:01.830
You're too kind.

07:01.830 --> 07:03.040
We're on the same side here.

07:03.040 --> 07:03.720
Here.

07:03.720 --> 07:05.850
Then you should definitely accept it.

07:09.550 --> 07:10.220
Fine.

07:10.740 --> 07:11.700
Alright.

07:25.610 --> 07:27.170
Seriously,

07:27.200 --> 07:28.890
you never tidy up.

07:28.910 --> 07:30.830
Look at how messy this place is.

07:31.360 --> 07:32.880
We're busy with work,

07:32.900 --> 07:34.430
and have no time to clean up.

07:35.820 --> 07:37.020
What about weekends?

07:37.370 --> 07:38.970
Are you busy on weekends too?

07:40.200 --> 07:41.400
Today's the weekend.

07:41.790 --> 07:42.990
Where's Zhenzhen?

07:43.230 --> 07:44.430
She went to the hotel.

07:44.580 --> 07:45.840
There's a reception at the hotel.

07:45.840 --> 07:46.900
She had to be there.

07:49.050 --> 07:51.220
I'm not saying she has to do housework.

07:51.630 --> 07:52.750
But she's pregnant

07:53.050 --> 07:54.800
and still running around outside.

07:54.800 --> 07:55.680
As a woman,

07:55.810 --> 07:57.810
how much work can she possibly have?

07:58.140 --> 07:59.950
You know her temper.

08:00.000 --> 08:01.130
She can't sit still.

08:01.140 --> 08:02.500
She likes to stay busy.

08:02.870 --> 08:04.890
If you made her stay home all day,

08:05.510 --> 08:06.930
she'd get all anxious

08:07.030 --> 08:08.400
and complain nonstop.

08:10.260 --> 08:12.140
You can't just indulge her.

08:12.940 --> 08:14.460
A woman's pregnancy lasts 10 months,

08:14.460 --> 08:16.190
and every single month is critical.

08:16.190 --> 08:17.920
She should stay home and rest.

08:18.700 --> 08:20.850
She's carrying our family's child.

08:20.880 --> 08:22.430
You can't be careless.

08:22.450 --> 08:23.570
Understand?

08:24.360 --> 08:25.650
Got it.

08:26.410 --> 08:28.270
You have to take my words to heart.

08:28.270 --> 08:29.270
Did you hear me?

08:29.290 --> 08:30.660
Yeah, I hear you.

08:31.060 --> 08:32.789
If it weren't for her

08:32.820 --> 08:34.250
being pregnant at that time,

08:34.250 --> 08:36.450
I'd never have let her into this family.

08:36.460 --> 08:38.110
Look at her frivolous face.

08:39.320 --> 08:40.960
She won't even stay home on weekends.

08:40.960 --> 08:41.750
Mom,

08:42.870 --> 08:44.550
you know, for a woman,

08:45.370 --> 08:47.540
isn't it good that she likes to work?

08:47.870 --> 08:49.360
Besides, I've told you,

08:49.790 --> 08:52.550
she has some connections I can use.

08:53.390 --> 08:54.710
Why should I go against her?

08:54.710 --> 08:56.370
Isn't it better to play along?

08:56.530 --> 08:58.690
Don't worry about your grandson.

08:58.720 --> 09:00.450
I will definitely protect him.

09:04.440 --> 09:05.390
You're back.

09:05.480 --> 09:06.200
When did you come back?

09:06.200 --> 09:06.910
I didn't hear you.

09:06.910 --> 09:07.820
Just now.

09:08.360 --> 09:10.690
Mom, Yucheng, what are you talking about?

09:11.060 --> 09:11.980
Nothing.

09:12.090 --> 09:13.890
I'm helping you tidy up the room.

09:13.920 --> 09:14.970
Let me do it.

09:15.030 --> 09:16.500
How could I let you clean?

09:16.520 --> 09:19.470
Zhenzhen, you've been busy all day.

09:19.520 --> 09:21.100
Go and get some rest.

09:21.240 --> 09:22.450
You don't need to help me.

09:22.450 --> 09:23.920
I'll be done soon.

09:29.510 --> 09:30.320
Mom,

09:30.640 --> 09:31.980
my colleague's looking for me.

09:31.980 --> 09:32.900
I have to go.

09:33.230 --> 09:34.180
Sorry I can't stay.

09:34.180 --> 09:35.910
Are you going out to work again?

09:36.090 --> 09:37.240
I got promoted.

09:37.380 --> 09:39.400
My colleagues want to celebrate with me.

09:39.400 --> 09:40.420
You got a promotion?

09:40.420 --> 09:41.540
Congratulations.

09:41.570 --> 09:42.700
I'll get going then.

09:43.020 --> 09:44.050
Stay safe.

09:44.990 --> 09:46.910
Take care on your way.

09:51.400 --> 09:52.630
Look at her.

10:17.210 --> 10:18.120
Hello, Mr. Cheng.

10:18.120 --> 10:19.320
Nice to see you again.

10:19.640 --> 10:21.040
You've got a good memory.

10:21.680 --> 10:22.370
By the way,

10:22.390 --> 10:24.660
this is our group's
North China regional head

10:24.660 --> 10:25.490
Mr. Dai.

10:25.970 --> 10:26.890
Hello, Mr. Dai.

10:26.910 --> 10:27.700
Hello.

10:27.880 --> 10:29.360
I've arranged a room
facing the sun for you.

10:29.360 --> 10:31.370
It has a better view. This way, please.

10:31.370 --> 10:33.490
But he hasn't checked in yet.

10:33.570 --> 10:35.560
That's okay.
We can drop off the luggage first.

10:35.560 --> 10:37.600
I'll have an attendant
come up and register later.

10:37.600 --> 10:38.480
Perfect.

10:38.850 --> 10:39.230
Let's go.

10:39.230 --> 10:39.870
Let's go.

10:44.790 --> 10:46.000
You can take a rest first.

10:46.000 --> 10:48.200
The attendant will be up
to see you shortly.

10:48.200 --> 10:49.130
Okay, thank you.

10:49.360 --> 10:50.000
Get some rest.

10:50.000 --> 10:51.300
Okay, bye.

10:54.200 --> 10:56.080
Mr. Cheng, let me walk you down.

10:56.080 --> 10:56.910
Okay.

10:57.090 --> 10:58.000
Thank you so much

10:58.000 --> 10:59.870
for introducing so many guests to us.

10:59.870 --> 11:00.720
Rest assured,

11:00.720 --> 11:01.790
our executive floor

11:01.790 --> 11:03.790
will wholeheartedly serve them.

11:04.000 --> 11:05.800
I trust you with them, of course.

11:07.140 --> 11:07.780
By the way,

11:08.000 --> 11:10.000
is the presidential suite
occupied right now?

11:10.000 --> 11:11.800
We have a long-term guest in one.

11:12.960 --> 11:14.320
But the other presidential suite

11:14.320 --> 11:15.120
is vacant.

11:15.120 --> 11:16.070
Whatever you need,

11:16.070 --> 11:17.000
just let me know.

11:18.000 --> 11:19.000
Here's the thing.

11:19.200 --> 11:21.910
A friend of mine is Li Bingyan's manager.

11:22.320 --> 11:23.240
Li Bingyan?

11:23.370 --> 11:25.090
You mean the actress Li Bingyan?

11:25.090 --> 11:26.370
Exactly.

11:26.480 --> 11:27.080
She's

11:27.080 --> 11:29.120
coming to Shanghai soon
to film a variety show.

11:29.120 --> 11:30.320
Her manager asked me

11:30.320 --> 11:32.000
to find a reliable hotel for her.

11:32.000 --> 11:34.370
The requirements: a presidential suite,

11:34.390 --> 11:35.270
and

11:35.300 --> 11:37.750
absolute confidentiality
regarding her schedule.

11:37.750 --> 11:39.910
Her personal life
absolutely cannot be disturbed.

11:39.910 --> 11:40.480
So the first place

11:40.480 --> 11:41.770
I thought of was your Purong Hotel,

11:41.770 --> 11:42.560
and I thought of you.

11:42.560 --> 11:44.680
I wonder if you're willing to take it.

11:44.710 --> 11:46.960
Yes, of course we are.

11:47.440 --> 11:49.680
But she's a celebrity

11:49.710 --> 11:51.020
with lots of public attention and fans.

11:51.020 --> 11:53.390
It's bound to come with
a fair amount of trouble.

11:53.390 --> 11:55.220
You have to consider the pressure.

11:55.220 --> 11:56.220
Don't worry.

11:56.290 --> 11:57.680
We will definitely try our best

11:57.680 --> 11:59.280
to meet all her needs.

11:59.320 --> 12:00.920
I'll set up a group chat then.

12:01.200 --> 12:01.960
Thank you.

12:01.960 --> 12:04.320
Don't mention it. I should thank you

12:04.320 --> 12:05.600
for always introducing such important VIPs

12:05.600 --> 12:06.600
to our hotel.

12:06.600 --> 12:09.060
It's all because of
the service you provide.

12:10.240 --> 12:10.720
Please.

12:10.800 --> 12:11.510
Please.

12:21.470 --> 12:22.440
Ms. Lu.

12:22.460 --> 12:23.220
Ms. Xu,

12:23.690 --> 12:25.290
I need a presidential suite.

12:25.290 --> 12:26.310
The VIP will arrive tomorrow.

12:26.310 --> 12:27.270
Please arrange it as soon as possible.

12:27.270 --> 12:28.200
I'm sorry,

12:28.200 --> 12:30.790
but the presidential suites
have just been booked.

12:30.790 --> 12:32.270
Then I suggest you figure something out

12:32.270 --> 12:33.570
and clear one quickly.

12:34.000 --> 12:35.000
This VIP has an agreement

12:35.000 --> 12:36.030
with our hotel.

12:36.140 --> 12:37.320
The accommodation must

12:37.320 --> 12:39.380
be no less than a presidential suite.

12:41.510 --> 12:43.450
[February 5, 2025]

12:41.670 --> 12:43.870
I'm sure you understand who this VIP is.

12:44.750 --> 12:46.590
If we fail to meet the VIP's needs,

12:46.590 --> 12:49.520
will you be responsible
for breaking the agreement?

12:49.690 --> 12:50.750
Whoever it is,

12:50.750 --> 12:52.150
she's indeed a step late.

12:52.390 --> 12:53.320
I'm sorry.

12:53.960 --> 12:54.910
Xu Miyu,

12:55.270 --> 12:56.820
why are you working against me?

12:56.820 --> 12:58.020
Let me put it this way.

12:58.020 --> 12:59.320
The room she stays in

12:59.520 --> 13:01.920
won't be vacant for the next 2 years.

13:01.940 --> 13:03.420
If this deal falls through

13:03.450 --> 13:04.450
because of you,

13:04.470 --> 13:06.870
can you afford
to cover the hotel's losses?

13:07.790 --> 13:09.670
Don't worry about my personal matters.

13:09.670 --> 13:11.910
But what I just said about
the presidential suite situation—

13:11.910 --> 13:13.200
that's the truth.

13:15.550 --> 13:18.240
Fine.
I won't make things difficult for you.

13:18.430 --> 13:19.920
If Mr. Ji asks about it,

13:19.950 --> 13:21.480
explain it to him yourself.

13:24.200 --> 13:26.190
Who does she think she is?

13:27.430 --> 13:31.500
[Reception]

13:29.000 --> 13:30.000
Let me check.

13:31.620 --> 13:35.260
[Room Status Center]

13:44.480 --> 13:45.030
Come in.

13:47.000 --> 13:47.790
Mr. Ji.

13:48.920 --> 13:51.080
I have something to discuss with you.

13:51.790 --> 13:52.550
Okay.

13:56.800 --> 13:58.200
The Qiao Feifei account

13:58.720 --> 14:00.750
is definitely an opportunity
for our hotel.

14:00.750 --> 14:01.750
I won't say

14:01.750 --> 14:04.000
how much effort it took me
to secure this order.

14:04.000 --> 14:04.750
And then

14:04.750 --> 14:06.870
Ms. Xu just shuts it down flat.

14:07.000 --> 14:08.840
Does she even have that authority?

14:08.840 --> 14:09.440
Alright.

14:09.750 --> 14:10.720
I got it.

14:11.030 --> 14:13.000
I'll look into the situation first.

14:13.000 --> 14:14.790
Leave this to me.

14:14.810 --> 14:16.860
Sorry to trouble you, Mr. Ji.

14:16.890 --> 14:17.800
Not at all.

14:23.000 --> 14:23.750
Actually,

14:23.750 --> 14:25.080
I shouldn't bother you

14:25.080 --> 14:26.480
with such a small matter.

14:27.120 --> 14:28.400
But I'm doing this

14:28.790 --> 14:30.480
for the benefit of the hotel.

14:38.950 --> 14:40.190
If there's nothing else,

14:40.190 --> 14:41.310
get back to work.

14:45.510 --> 14:46.360
Okay.

15:04.400 --> 15:05.680
♪Ah♪

15:06.570 --> 15:09.470
♪Talking to myself♪

15:11.290 --> 15:12.590
♪Ah♪

15:13.220 --> 15:17.710
♪Playing pretend
that I've got it together♪

15:16.170 --> 15:17.060
Stop watching.

15:17.090 --> 15:17.910
Hurry up and clean.

15:17.910 --> 15:18.950
The guest will be here any minute.

15:18.950 --> 15:21.170
♪ That fleeting moment I tried to hold ♪

15:21.860 --> 15:24.860
♪ Let it go when the glass runs dry ♪

15:22.870 --> 15:24.530
Who's this?

15:25.410 --> 15:27.360
You don't know Qiao Feifei?

15:25.870 --> 15:28.900
♪ Unfinished longings ♪

15:27.390 --> 15:29.520
You've never watched the show Star Maker?

15:29.520 --> 15:30.590
I haven't missed a single episode.

15:29.770 --> 15:32.560
♪ Drift like fading embers ♪

15:30.670 --> 15:32.220
That's her hit song.

15:32.250 --> 15:33.450
The VIP is arriving soon.

15:33.450 --> 15:34.870
How's the cleaning going?

15:34.340 --> 15:36.090
♪ Still longing for yesterday's glow ♪

15:36.710 --> 15:37.500
Almost done.

15:37.020 --> 15:39.800
♪ Yet sailing into
the ocean's depths at night ♪

15:41.010 --> 15:43.420
♪ Questions without answers ♪

15:41.360 --> 15:42.690
You two, stop watching.

15:43.790 --> 15:44.720
Hurry and clean up.

15:44.720 --> 15:46.250
The guest is arriving soon.

15:47.310 --> 15:48.830
Hurry up, Jia.

16:01.960 --> 16:02.960
Thank you.

16:07.560 --> 16:08.280
Huanhuan.

16:08.300 --> 16:10.060
Have you seen Ms. Li Bingyan?

16:12.300 --> 16:13.390
I'm here.

16:19.780 --> 16:20.670
Hello, Ms. Li.

16:20.670 --> 16:22.530
I'm your butler. My surname is Xu.

16:23.510 --> 16:25.080
Hello, I'm Li Bingyan.

16:27.200 --> 16:29.120
Your name is Xu Miyu?

16:29.610 --> 16:31.200
It's a really nice name.

16:31.220 --> 16:33.150
You don't put on any airs as a star.

16:34.010 --> 16:35.430
I'm not really a star.

16:35.540 --> 16:36.110
Let's go.

16:36.130 --> 16:37.130
This way, please.

16:38.550 --> 16:39.280
I'll take it.

16:39.920 --> 16:40.760
Thank you.

16:52.390 --> 16:53.320
Li Bingyan?

16:54.550 --> 16:55.390
Mr. Duan.

16:57.250 --> 16:58.800
I... I'm your fan.

16:59.280 --> 17:00.640
You must be Mr. Duan Jr.

17:01.140 --> 17:01.900
Hello.

17:02.870 --> 17:03.840
You know me?

17:03.840 --> 17:05.960
W-Well, I'm so honored.

17:06.680 --> 17:08.069
Can I have your autograph?

17:08.069 --> 17:08.680
Sure.

17:08.680 --> 17:09.660
Well...

17:09.680 --> 17:10.589
Pen.

17:12.290 --> 17:13.819
I don't have a pen, Mr. Duan.

17:15.680 --> 17:16.890
How about a photo?

17:16.910 --> 17:18.099
What a coincidence.

17:18.119 --> 17:18.950
I'm sorry.

17:19.030 --> 17:20.920
I'm not wearing makeup today.

17:21.160 --> 17:23.160
It's not convenient to take photos.

17:24.190 --> 17:26.050
Mr. Duan, the guest needs to rest.

17:26.400 --> 17:27.290
I'm sorry.

17:27.319 --> 17:28.600
Where is my room?

17:29.020 --> 17:29.610
This way, please.

17:29.610 --> 17:30.210
Okay.

17:31.390 --> 17:33.830
-We could at least chat.
-Mr. Duan.

17:34.000 --> 17:34.900
I'm sorry.

17:37.000 --> 17:38.240
Xu Miyu.

17:41.160 --> 17:42.020
I remember you.

17:44.010 --> 17:44.870
Please come in.

18:01.720 --> 18:03.200
This is your room.

18:03.200 --> 18:04.880
If you need anything later,

18:04.880 --> 18:06.960
just call the number on the bedside.

18:06.960 --> 18:08.690
We're at your service anytime.

18:10.960 --> 18:13.020
Thank you for helping me out just now.

18:13.120 --> 18:15.840
I actually have a bit of social anxiety.

18:16.020 --> 18:17.020
I understand.

18:17.040 --> 18:18.210
The more public a figure is,

18:18.210 --> 18:20.070
the more private space they need.

18:20.850 --> 18:21.570
Thank you.

18:22.410 --> 18:24.220
You're really sharp.

18:24.240 --> 18:25.100
I'm flattered.

18:26.200 --> 18:28.300
If there's anything I need—

18:28.590 --> 18:29.750
well,

18:29.750 --> 18:32.240
I don't sleep very well,

18:32.280 --> 18:34.800
so I'm quite picky about
the living environment.

18:34.800 --> 18:35.680
I'm especially sensitive to noise.

18:35.680 --> 18:37.960
We'll keep the hallway
as quiet as possible.

18:37.960 --> 18:41.720
Also, I could add some
begonia to your room's diffuser.

18:41.720 --> 18:44.200
Begonia helps
calm the mind and promotes sleep.

18:44.200 --> 18:46.400
And having floral scent in the room

18:46.400 --> 18:47.920
will also make you feel relaxed.

18:47.920 --> 18:49.400
Thank you, Ms. Xu.

18:49.680 --> 18:50.510
You seem like

18:50.510 --> 18:52.910
someone who's very considerate of others.

18:53.750 --> 18:54.720
Please get some rest.

18:54.720 --> 18:55.680
I'll go prepare it right away.

18:55.680 --> 18:56.200
Okay.

19:16.090 --> 19:17.750
Send the diffuser up now,

19:17.750 --> 19:18.680
before the lunch break.

19:18.680 --> 19:19.480
Okay.

19:19.480 --> 19:20.160
Here.

19:22.030 --> 19:23.810
Everyone, pay attention.

19:24.060 --> 19:25.680
Ms. Li doesn't sleep well,

19:25.680 --> 19:27.030
as I reminded you before.

19:27.030 --> 19:28.830
So when we go upstairs to serve,

19:28.830 --> 19:29.680
we must keep quiet.

19:29.680 --> 19:30.310
Got it?

19:30.310 --> 19:30.900
Yes.

19:31.290 --> 19:32.040
Ms. Xu.

19:32.070 --> 19:34.240
Ms. Lu is pushing
for the presidential suite again.

19:34.240 --> 19:35.110
Got it.

19:39.620 --> 19:41.210
Hello. Is Mr. Duan here?

19:41.760 --> 19:42.710
Come in.

19:46.670 --> 19:47.510
Sorry to disturb you, Mr. Duan.

19:47.510 --> 19:48.510
I'm Xu Miyu.

19:48.980 --> 19:51.640
There's something
I'd like to discuss with you.

19:51.640 --> 19:53.000
We just saw each other.

19:53.060 --> 19:54.460
What's there to disturb?

19:56.090 --> 19:56.960
Here's the thing.

19:56.960 --> 19:59.320
Our presidential suites
are fully occupied.

19:59.320 --> 20:01.790
And now another VIP wants to check in.

20:01.880 --> 20:04.430
So there's a bit of a conflict.

20:04.450 --> 20:05.690
Sounds troublesome.

20:06.120 --> 20:07.270
So what do we do?

20:07.510 --> 20:10.790
Mr. Duan, that's why I wanted

20:10.790 --> 20:12.550
to ask you...

20:14.000 --> 20:15.110
To move out?

20:15.110 --> 20:15.920
Not moving out.

20:15.920 --> 20:18.000
Just to have you temporarily
stay on the executive floor.

20:18.000 --> 20:19.720
And once this guest leaves,

20:19.720 --> 20:20.850
you can move back in.

20:21.950 --> 20:23.880
Then for such a big favor,

20:24.640 --> 20:25.840
how will you repay me?

20:27.070 --> 20:29.240
You're the financial backer
of Purong Hotel.

20:29.240 --> 20:31.550
If the hotel's performance is good,

20:31.570 --> 20:32.920
you can also get

20:32.920 --> 20:34.200
a higher return on investment.

20:34.200 --> 20:35.200
Enough.

20:35.200 --> 20:36.200
Drop the corporate talk.

20:36.200 --> 20:37.030
It's boring.

20:37.340 --> 20:40.400
Can't you humble yourself a bit
when asking for a favor?

20:41.650 --> 20:43.200
W-Why don't you ask me

20:43.200 --> 20:44.200
what I want?

20:45.010 --> 20:46.320
What do you want?

20:47.880 --> 20:50.710
Then I have to think about it carefully.

20:53.780 --> 20:55.180
What do you have to offer?

20:55.780 --> 20:56.580
I...

21:00.110 --> 21:00.960
Hello, Mr. Ji.

21:02.920 --> 21:03.510
Where is Ms. Xu?

21:03.510 --> 21:04.400
She's not here.

21:04.400 --> 21:05.530
She's in the presidential suite.

21:05.530 --> 21:06.530
Which one?

21:06.590 --> 21:07.790
Mr. Duan's suite.

21:07.790 --> 21:09.720
They're discussing the room swap.

21:09.960 --> 21:11.000
Okay, thanks.

21:12.720 --> 21:15.240
I'm not asking you
to get me the stars from the sky.

21:15.240 --> 21:16.590
Doesn't she just live across the hall?

21:16.590 --> 21:17.680
You go knock on her door

21:17.680 --> 21:18.680
and introduce me.

21:18.910 --> 21:20.160
Am I that unpresentable?

21:20.160 --> 21:21.310
I don't mean that, Mr. Duan.

21:21.310 --> 21:22.630
Take a step back.

21:22.660 --> 21:24.260
I could knock on her door

21:24.280 --> 21:25.540
and recommend myself.

21:25.630 --> 21:27.280
And you're still trying to stop me.

21:27.280 --> 21:29.080
Did she buy you out or something?

21:29.220 --> 21:30.960
The guest across the hall clearly told me

21:30.960 --> 21:32.640
that she didn't want
to be disturbed by anyone.

21:32.640 --> 21:33.960
As her butler,

21:33.960 --> 21:34.480
I...

21:34.480 --> 21:36.220
You really think you're something?

21:36.220 --> 21:37.350
You're her butler,

21:37.350 --> 21:38.480
but you're not mine?

21:38.790 --> 21:39.640
I don't care.

21:40.320 --> 21:42.120
You have to ask her out for me.

21:42.140 --> 21:44.140
I'm having dinner with her tonight.

21:44.880 --> 21:45.710
I promise you!

21:50.360 --> 21:51.670
The knight is here.

21:51.690 --> 21:53.410
We were just having a good chat.

21:53.410 --> 21:55.740
There is a lot to do
on the executive floor.

21:55.750 --> 21:57.650
Tell me if you need anything.

22:07.590 --> 22:08.550
Interesting.

22:08.950 --> 22:11.020
[Qiao Feifei, Chinese actress, singer]

22:11.020 --> 22:11.480
[Qiao Feifei, a new-generation
idol female star in China]

22:11.510 --> 22:12.030
[Qiao Feifei's efforts and talent
have enabled her to rise rapidly]

22:12.050 --> 22:12.590
[in the entertainment industry, leading
among the new generation of idols.]

22:12.670 --> 22:13.970
[Chinese name Qiao Feifei]
[Alias: Feifei]

22:17.180 --> 22:18.020
Mr. Ji.

22:18.680 --> 22:19.960
The presidential suite has been vacated.

22:19.960 --> 22:21.100
Have someone clean it up.

22:21.100 --> 22:22.300
That's great, Mr. Ji.

22:22.380 --> 22:23.510
How did you get Mr. Duan

22:23.510 --> 22:25.170
to move out so quickly?

22:25.190 --> 22:27.760
I gave him a ticket to the fashion gala.

22:27.790 --> 22:30.130
He gets to walk the red carpet
with his idol.

22:30.130 --> 22:31.660
Walk the red carpet?

22:32.000 --> 22:33.990
Will Ms. Li cooperate?

22:34.060 --> 22:36.030
That's not my concern.

22:36.060 --> 22:38.190
We'll have to see what he's capable of.

22:39.130 --> 22:40.170
I didn't expect

22:40.500 --> 22:42.430
you had such tricks up your sleeve.

22:43.200 --> 22:44.510
Your compliments are the greatest

22:44.510 --> 22:45.510
encouragement for my work.

22:45.510 --> 22:46.110
Thank you.

22:46.110 --> 22:48.400
Are you playing tricks again?

22:49.960 --> 22:52.360
I didn't expect
you held grudges like that.

23:03.700 --> 23:04.380
Mr. Duan.

23:14.640 --> 23:15.700
You messed with me?

23:16.460 --> 23:17.720
What's wrong, Mr. Duan?

23:17.720 --> 23:20.270
Didn't you have a good chat
with Li Bingyan?

23:20.270 --> 23:21.200
Chat?

23:21.440 --> 23:23.310
She kicked me away
as soon as she got on the red carpet.

23:23.310 --> 23:24.680
We didn't even say hi.

23:25.140 --> 23:27.580
That's really a pity.

23:28.460 --> 23:29.830
I feel pity for you,

23:30.230 --> 23:32.650
because our cooperation ends here.

23:32.670 --> 23:34.530
I'm telling you I'm very unhappy.

23:34.720 --> 23:35.510
Also,

23:35.790 --> 23:37.710
compared to the ordinary
leather on this executive floor,

23:37.710 --> 23:39.940
I prefer the genuine leather sofa
in my presidential suite.

23:39.940 --> 23:40.880
Mr. Duan,

23:41.360 --> 23:43.120
our deal is not over yet.

23:46.200 --> 23:47.240
Do you know

23:47.270 --> 23:48.680
who is currently staying

23:48.680 --> 23:49.960
in Room 1816?

23:50.960 --> 23:51.750
Who?

23:51.880 --> 23:52.720
Zuo Qiang.

23:53.510 --> 23:54.470
You know him?

23:54.510 --> 23:56.350
He's your dad's right-hand man.

23:56.380 --> 23:57.960
Everyone in the circle knows him.

23:57.960 --> 23:59.510
Then... what is he doing here?

23:59.510 --> 24:01.560
We don't know what he's here for.

24:01.590 --> 24:03.690
But now that you've
moved to the executive floor.

24:03.690 --> 24:05.860
Keeping a low profile
certainly won't hurt.

24:05.860 --> 24:06.900
You don't want him

24:06.930 --> 24:08.810
to snitch on you to your dad

24:08.830 --> 24:10.700
that you spend your days
in Purong Hotel's presidential suite

24:10.700 --> 24:11.760
having fun, right?

24:13.200 --> 24:14.530
You knew this all along?

24:14.640 --> 24:15.890
I just found out.

24:19.560 --> 24:21.490
Well, since you're so thoughtful,

24:22.020 --> 24:23.820
I won't embarrass you this time.

24:24.470 --> 24:26.330
Thank you for your great support.

24:33.600 --> 24:34.970
Don't get too cocky.

24:34.990 --> 24:37.720
We'll have plenty of time
to deal with each other.

24:37.880 --> 24:39.590
Thank you for going easy on me.

25:16.180 --> 25:17.170
Welcome.

25:17.200 --> 25:18.230
Welcome.

25:26.430 --> 25:27.510
Qingping.

25:27.570 --> 25:30.240
Get two more people down
to help with the luggage.

25:30.240 --> 25:31.570
Stop looking. Let's go.

25:35.730 --> 25:36.940
Wei.

25:37.360 --> 25:39.360
You look even more handsome today.

25:40.520 --> 25:41.450
Zhenzhen,

25:41.530 --> 25:43.980
I'm only here as a favor to you.

25:44.410 --> 25:46.440
You must take good care of our Feifei.

25:46.440 --> 25:47.850
Thank you so much, Wei.

25:48.120 --> 25:49.300
Feifei,

25:49.530 --> 25:52.000
you're 100 times prettier
in person than on screen.

25:52.000 --> 25:53.640
Besides, you're a top star

25:53.640 --> 25:55.590
and a ratings queen everyone knows.

25:55.590 --> 25:56.830
Our hotel will definitely provide

25:56.830 --> 25:58.000
first-class service.

25:58.000 --> 25:59.280
Please rest assured, Wei.

25:59.280 --> 26:00.480
Otherwise, Feifei's fans

26:00.480 --> 26:02.080
wouldn't let us off the hook.

26:02.440 --> 26:03.240
Please.

26:07.070 --> 26:08.810
Isn't this the concierge's job?

26:08.810 --> 26:09.310
Ms. Xu,

26:09.310 --> 26:11.200
why bringing the luggage over yourself?

26:11.200 --> 26:12.620
Are you a fan too?

26:12.770 --> 26:14.160
There's a lot of luggage
for the presidential suite.

26:14.160 --> 26:15.960
The HSKP Department is helping out.

26:15.960 --> 26:17.680
Any problem with that, Ms. Lu?

26:17.680 --> 26:18.510
No problem at all.

26:18.510 --> 26:19.780
You're quite right.

26:19.900 --> 26:22.110
Helping guests is also your job.

26:28.860 --> 26:29.880
Be careful, everyone.

26:29.880 --> 26:31.340
Don't bump into anything.

26:31.590 --> 26:34.250
You can't afford to pay
for such valuable items.

26:38.900 --> 26:39.610
Ms. Xu.

26:39.920 --> 26:40.550
Ms. Xu.

26:41.190 --> 26:42.240
Should we book the small banquet hall

26:42.240 --> 26:43.350
or a private dining room for lunch?

26:43.350 --> 26:44.240
The kitchen's asking

26:44.240 --> 26:45.490
how many people
they need to prepare food for.

26:45.490 --> 26:47.290
I'll let you know once I confirm.

26:47.510 --> 26:48.270
Ms. Xu,

26:48.270 --> 26:49.960
can you get someone from
the Engineering Department to come over?

26:49.960 --> 26:51.110
We need to connect
some external equipment,

26:51.110 --> 26:52.550
and check the voltage.

26:52.550 --> 26:53.590
Okay, wait a moment.

26:53.590 --> 26:54.640
Ms. Xu. Ms. Xu.

26:54.640 --> 26:57.180
Can you help me ask
about the number of diners first?

26:57.180 --> 26:58.640
Do you have a piano here?

26:58.640 --> 26:59.390
Ou!

26:59.640 --> 27:01.400
Ou, Feifei asked you to go in.

27:01.400 --> 27:02.400
Tell her to wait a moment.

27:02.400 --> 27:03.200
Ms. Xu!

27:03.570 --> 27:05.590
There seems to be a problem
with their credit card.

27:05.590 --> 27:06.550
Could you double-check for me?

27:06.550 --> 27:07.750
Is this the right one?

27:07.920 --> 27:10.650
Ms. Xu, the guest in the presidential suite
complained about the noise.

27:10.650 --> 27:11.300
Got it.

27:12.020 --> 27:12.990
Ms. Xu, that...

27:14.660 --> 27:16.330
I've heard everyone's questions.

27:16.330 --> 27:17.850
This is a public area.

27:17.880 --> 27:19.550
Please don't make loud noises.

27:19.550 --> 27:20.790
There are VIPs resting.

27:20.790 --> 27:22.410
Go back to your rooms and close the doors.

27:22.410 --> 27:23.800
I'll come find you in a moment.

27:23.800 --> 27:24.780
You, you, and you,

27:24.780 --> 27:26.170
go wait for me on the executive floor.

27:26.170 --> 27:28.270
I'll come find you
after sorting out the luggage.

27:28.270 --> 27:28.830
Okay?

27:28.950 --> 27:29.270
Okay.

27:29.270 --> 27:29.640
Okay.

27:29.640 --> 27:30.970
No problem. Dismissed.

27:31.330 --> 27:32.400
Miyu,

27:32.830 --> 27:34.230
I'll go get an autograph.

27:35.360 --> 27:36.490
It's working hours.

27:36.510 --> 27:37.590
Sort out the luggage first.

27:37.590 --> 27:39.070
But my idol is right inside.

27:39.070 --> 27:41.400
Work first. You'll get your chance later.

27:43.030 --> 27:45.790
Ms. Xu, the presidential suite guests
sent their thanks.

27:45.790 --> 27:46.660
Got it.

27:49.070 --> 27:49.600
Let's go.

27:51.830 --> 27:54.240
Right now, we have two celebrities
staying in the presidential suites.

27:54.240 --> 27:55.770
Qiao Feifei and Li Bingyan.

27:58.550 --> 28:00.030
As public figures, they naturally

28:00.030 --> 28:01.770
have higher demands

28:01.800 --> 28:03.310
for privacy and security.

28:03.400 --> 28:05.160
I hope everyone will keep this in mind

28:05.160 --> 28:06.270
and act accordingly.

28:06.270 --> 28:09.030
Don't wait until their teams
come to complain

28:09.030 --> 28:10.270
before we scramble to respond.

28:10.270 --> 28:11.000
In that case,

28:11.000 --> 28:12.310
it would be beneath Purong Hotel's

28:12.310 --> 28:13.270
service standards.

28:13.270 --> 28:14.850
Then what's the best way to handle this?

28:14.850 --> 28:17.050
Should we send more people up to patrol?

28:17.550 --> 28:19.480
The celebrities don't want
to be disturbed in the first place.

28:19.480 --> 28:20.750
Sending more people to wander around

28:20.750 --> 28:22.410
is just asking to be yelled at.

28:23.200 --> 28:24.030
Ms. Xu,

28:24.510 --> 28:26.110
I think the key to this issue

28:26.110 --> 28:27.920
is to resolve the review mechanism

28:27.920 --> 28:29.250
on our executive floor.

28:29.360 --> 28:31.900
Everyone who takes the elevator
to the presidential suite

28:31.900 --> 28:33.560
should be strictly registered.

28:33.560 --> 28:34.680
This way, we can manage

28:34.680 --> 28:36.330
the flow in and out
of the presidential suite

28:36.330 --> 28:38.460
and ensure
the guests' privacy isn't disturbed.

28:38.460 --> 28:39.640
That's a very good idea.

28:39.640 --> 28:42.100
Qingping, I'm putting you
in charge of this.

28:42.110 --> 28:42.790
Okay.

28:43.130 --> 28:46.240
Also, if any fans come
looking for the celebrities,

28:46.270 --> 28:47.640
we must remember:

28:47.660 --> 28:49.140
no verbal conflicts

28:49.170 --> 28:50.060
or violent eviction.

28:50.060 --> 28:51.260
We're service staff.

28:51.580 --> 28:53.690
Our job is to keep the executive floor

28:53.720 --> 28:54.790
and the presidential suite

28:54.790 --> 28:57.090
safe, smooth, and peaceful.

28:57.120 --> 28:58.940
We cannot afford to cause any conflict.

28:58.940 --> 29:00.140
Got it?

29:00.270 --> 29:00.880
Yes.

29:00.880 --> 29:01.640
Okay.

29:01.640 --> 29:02.570
Get back to work.

29:10.770 --> 29:11.640
As always,

29:11.710 --> 29:13.910
I'll serve you two the Yan Du Xian first.

29:25.880 --> 29:26.640
Thank you.

29:28.550 --> 29:29.680
Enjoy your meal.

29:45.610 --> 29:47.030
Is the gluten ball
stuffed with meat ready?

29:47.030 --> 29:47.640
Yes.

29:47.640 --> 29:49.290
How much longer
for the shredded pork and ham soup?

29:49.290 --> 29:50.230
Almost done.

29:52.780 --> 29:53.780
Chef,

29:53.800 --> 29:55.600
a lot of tables
are asking for their dishes.

29:55.600 --> 29:56.440
-Got it.
-Thank you.

29:56.440 --> 29:57.000
Okay.

29:59.270 --> 30:00.580
Where's Chef Yang?

30:01.170 --> 30:02.630
I said, where's Chef Yang?

30:02.640 --> 30:04.170
Chef Yang went to make soup.

30:16.200 --> 30:17.150
Qiaoqi,

30:17.180 --> 30:19.270
Ting from the restaurant just told me

30:19.270 --> 30:22.520
that Professor Liu and his wife canceled
their reservation for next week.

30:22.520 --> 30:24.180
Was it the food or the service?

30:24.480 --> 30:27.810
They said there's a problem
with the taste of the Yan Du Xian.

30:46.200 --> 30:47.440
When did this run out?

30:48.160 --> 30:49.030
I don't know.

30:55.570 --> 30:58.310
Why didn't anyone tell me
we were out of cured pork?

30:58.310 --> 30:59.110
You didn't ask.

30:59.110 --> 31:00.640
What kind of answer is that?

31:00.660 --> 31:02.480
How do you make Yan Du Xian
without cured pork?

31:02.480 --> 31:03.160
You...

31:04.200 --> 31:06.570
Where's your name tag?
Why aren't you wearing it?

31:06.570 --> 31:08.100
I'm not wearing it. So what?

31:08.810 --> 31:10.600
You never call me by my name anyway.

31:10.600 --> 31:11.900
Don't you always call me

31:11.900 --> 31:12.820
"Hey?"

31:13.260 --> 31:14.700
Baozi, say less.

31:14.720 --> 31:15.850
Come help me.

31:17.810 --> 31:18.990
Stop looking.

31:19.010 --> 31:20.140
Get back to cooking.

31:21.590 --> 31:22.270
Eight-Treasure Duck!

31:22.270 --> 31:23.070
Four Joy Meatballs!

31:23.070 --> 31:25.310
Braised Pork Intestines and Yan Du Xian!

31:25.310 --> 31:26.720
Yan Du Xian again.

31:28.200 --> 31:29.160
Use

31:29.430 --> 31:30.760
air-dried pork for now.

31:31.440 --> 31:32.270
Okay.

31:44.750 --> 31:47.160
Excuse me, what meat is this?

31:47.680 --> 31:48.610
Air-dried pork.

31:49.550 --> 31:52.270
And what season
is the air-dried pork meant for?

31:52.640 --> 31:53.470
Summer.

31:54.680 --> 31:56.480
So you use summer air-dried pork,

31:56.480 --> 31:59.510
mix in some leftover autumn ham scraps,

31:59.720 --> 32:01.070
and slap together

32:01.310 --> 32:03.170
a half-decent spring Yan Du Xian.

32:03.850 --> 32:05.160
Is your Purong Hotel

32:05.190 --> 32:07.310
trying to ruin its own name?

32:09.200 --> 32:11.470
Don't our loyal customers' palates

32:12.030 --> 32:14.160
deserve a little more effort from you?

32:15.870 --> 32:17.030
I'm sorry, sir.

32:17.050 --> 32:18.450
It's my responsibility.

32:24.730 --> 32:27.430
[Soups] [Bamboo shoot soup
with fresh and pickled streaky pork]

32:27.530 --> 32:29.090
When did the cured pork supply run out?

32:29.090 --> 32:29.960
Last week.

32:30.700 --> 32:33.000
They made it clear
they only work with Chef Jia.

32:33.000 --> 32:35.410
But I'm already looking for new suppliers.

32:35.440 --> 32:37.300
Please give me a little more time.

32:38.070 --> 32:39.680
It will be difficult
during this special period,

32:39.680 --> 32:41.690
but please hang in there, Chef Li.

32:41.720 --> 32:42.510
I have faith in you.

32:42.510 --> 32:44.040
I won't let you down, Mr. Ji.

32:44.530 --> 32:47.330
We absolutely cannot
let our signature dish fail.

32:49.550 --> 32:52.150
Let me know
when there's something good to eat.

32:52.680 --> 32:53.530
You got it.

34:16.600 --> 34:17.520
Xu Miyu!

34:20.340 --> 34:21.870
Where are you going so late?

34:21.920 --> 34:23.179
I'm going to the hotel.

34:23.510 --> 34:25.179
There's something I need to do.

34:25.179 --> 34:26.310
Is everything okay?

34:29.239 --> 34:33.949
[Bund Tunnel]

34:37.960 --> 34:38.719
You're here.

34:38.760 --> 34:41.949
[Staff Only]

34:39.670 --> 34:41.810
How is it? Smells good, right?

34:42.270 --> 34:44.270
Makes your mouth water, doesn't it?

34:46.750 --> 34:47.790
Miyu...

34:48.400 --> 34:49.679
You scared me.

34:49.699 --> 34:50.739
Why is it you?

34:50.800 --> 34:52.230
I saw the light in the kitchen.

34:52.230 --> 34:52.760
So I came to check.

34:52.760 --> 34:54.420
Why haven't you left work yet?

34:58.920 --> 35:00.760
Where did you get the cured pork?

35:02.170 --> 35:03.170
Smells so good.

35:05.250 --> 35:06.910
Let me taste it for the guests.

35:08.000 --> 35:09.380
Is it for you?

35:09.580 --> 35:11.170
-Qiaoqi.
-Then who's it for?

35:11.170 --> 35:11.920
You're here.

35:12.400 --> 35:13.650
You invited Xu Miyu?

35:14.220 --> 35:15.950
Let's both try it. You go first.

35:18.680 --> 35:20.530
Why are you here?

35:21.030 --> 35:21.880
Mr. Ji.

35:22.070 --> 35:24.190
Did you invite Mr. Ji?

35:24.230 --> 35:24.930
No, no.

35:24.960 --> 35:26.720
We ran into each other on the way.

35:26.720 --> 35:29.720
Didn't I tell you to let me know
when there's good food?

35:30.160 --> 35:31.330
This is just a test.

35:31.360 --> 35:32.590
I don't know how it will turn out.

35:32.590 --> 35:34.520
So I wanted Miyu to help me check it.

35:35.510 --> 35:37.000
As an experienced foodie,

35:37.280 --> 35:38.610
I can help with that too.

35:38.630 --> 35:39.670
So can I.

35:42.180 --> 35:43.510
Then let's all try it.

35:45.590 --> 35:46.590
It smells so good.

35:52.320 --> 35:54.920
Earthy from the clay pot,
a hint of charcoal,

35:55.070 --> 35:56.830
with a little bit of smokiness.

35:56.880 --> 35:59.150
Tomorrow we can use this Yan Du Xian

35:59.150 --> 36:00.510
to blow the diners away.

36:00.870 --> 36:02.190
It can definitely become our

36:02.190 --> 36:04.070
new signature dish at Purong Hotel.

36:04.070 --> 36:05.510
Keep bragging.

36:05.550 --> 36:08.010
It's not up to you
whether the guests like it.

36:08.280 --> 36:09.740
I'm really not confident.

36:10.040 --> 36:11.510
After all, Chef Jia's Yan Du Xian

36:11.510 --> 36:13.000
dominates Shanghai.

36:13.240 --> 36:15.570
Many guests come here for its reputation.

36:17.030 --> 36:19.480
Will the Chinese restaurant
really be ruined in my hands?

36:19.480 --> 36:22.560
The quality of Yan Du Xian
must certainly continue to improve.

36:22.560 --> 36:24.070
But does it have to be exactly the same

36:24.070 --> 36:25.070
as Chef Jia's?

36:25.310 --> 36:26.310
I don't think so.

36:26.590 --> 36:27.320
Times change,

36:27.320 --> 36:28.960
and so do diners' tastes.

36:29.360 --> 36:31.000
Now that Chef Jia has blocked

36:31.000 --> 36:31.880
all supply channels,

36:31.880 --> 36:33.510
we can find another way.

36:33.560 --> 36:34.670
Let's see if there

36:34.860 --> 36:36.630
are other possibilities for this dish.

36:36.630 --> 36:37.470
Okay, Mr. Ji.

36:37.510 --> 36:38.760
Tomorrow, I'll keep looking

36:38.760 --> 36:40.230
for cured pork suppliers.

36:42.220 --> 36:43.240
I'll help you.

36:43.510 --> 36:44.510
There are plenty of

36:44.510 --> 36:47.140
cured pork makers
in the Yangtze River Delta.

36:47.170 --> 36:49.290
We can definitely find a good source.

36:49.320 --> 36:50.960
Leave it to me.

36:51.000 --> 36:52.510
Stop bragging.

36:52.510 --> 36:54.670
It'd be great
if you don't make things worse.

36:54.670 --> 36:55.510
See?

36:57.000 --> 36:58.360
You always put me down.

37:01.800 --> 37:03.030
One last bowl.

37:14.760 --> 37:15.780
Yan Du Xian.

37:16.690 --> 37:17.810
Please enjoy.

37:22.280 --> 37:23.070
Hello?

37:24.540 --> 37:25.190
Okay.

37:25.210 --> 37:26.270
I'll be right back.

37:40.480 --> 37:42.310
Waiter, I'd like to order!

37:47.190 --> 37:47.960
Hello, sir.

37:47.960 --> 37:49.120
What would you like to eat?

37:49.120 --> 37:50.680
One Yan Du Xian.

37:51.360 --> 37:52.880
Anything else, sir?

37:52.900 --> 37:53.670
No, thanks.

38:04.700 --> 38:05.840
[Trending]

38:06.240 --> 38:09.450
[Former Purong Hotel's Head Chef
Jia Shikun Joins Kuanli]

38:13.530 --> 38:15.250
[Former Purong Hotel's Head Chef
Jia Shikun Joins Kuanli]

38:17.080 --> 38:17.300
[Former Purong Hotel's Head Chef
Jia Shikun Joins Kuanli]

38:18.220 --> 38:19.790
[Ji Feng]

38:19.820 --> 38:22.480
[Photos and videos]

38:22.510 --> 38:23.320
[Ji Feng]

38:26.840 --> 38:28.000
[WeChat]

38:28.100 --> 38:29.200
[Chef Qiao]

38:31.570 --> 38:33.510
[Chef Qiao]

38:32.170 --> 38:33.450
Are things going well?

38:41.460 --> 38:43.390
Is the Yan Du Xian's response good?

38:53.460 --> 38:54.590
Watch the heat.

38:57.080 --> 39:03.340
[Xue Rui]
[Is the Yan Du Xian's response good?]

39:02.330 --> 39:03.100
Pretty good.

39:04.990 --> 39:06.180
Move faster.

39:06.200 --> 39:06.550
Okay.

39:06.550 --> 39:07.230
Everything okay?

39:07.230 --> 39:08.550
Qiaoqi, Qiaoqi!

39:08.550 --> 39:10.110
A customer is causing trouble
in the Chinese restaurant.
